The paper presents a probabilistic planner that incorporates heuristics and deals with partial-order planning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Programming Languages (cs.PL) categories. The planner also deals with robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG) due to its probabilistic nature. Finally, the paper discusses the design and implementation of the planner, which falls under the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category.
